  <div class="mac-password">
  <h5>3. Does your computer have a login password?</h5>
    <select name="password">
        <option value="yes">Yes</option>
        <option value="no">No</option>
        <option value="not sure">I'm Not Sure</option>
        <option value="unknown">I don't know what a login password is</option>
    </select>
  </div><br><br>

  <div class="mac-cookies">
  <h5>4. When was the last time you cleared your cookies?</h5>
